rows.name: Ask Nopopon if he's heard any interesting rumors.

rows.label: tev056101_SEL0061
rows.name: Ask Nopopon if he's heard any interesting rumors.

rows.label: tev056101_MSG0001
rows.name:
Divine Nopopon was curious about friend's city and
deigned to visit.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056101_MSG0002
rows.name:
Holy spirits not allowed to meddle in mortal affairs,
so Divine Nopopon must watch from afar.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056101_MSG0003
rows.name:
But Divine Nopopon believes that friend will bring
peace to city one day![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056101_MSG0004
rows.name: May you succeed at every nopopportunity![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056101_MSG0007
rows.name:
Somewhere in Mira, friend will find another creature
just as round as Divine Nopopon. Do not be fooled![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056101_MSG0008
rows.name:
Impostor looks roly-poly, but has black heart!
Friend should be careful if paths ever cross.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056101_MSG0009
rows.name:
...Friend look like friend who wants to know identity
of impostor.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056101_MSG0010
rows.name:
But friend must discover this for self.
That is way of world![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056101_MSG0011
rows.name:
Divine Nopopon imagines friend knows this as well as
anyone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056101_MSG0012
rows.name: May you succeed at every nopopportunity![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056101_MSG0026
rows.name:
Ah... Divine Nopopon senses that friend has already
crossed paths with roly-poly impostor creature.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056101_MSG0027
rows.name:
But friend need not say another word!
Some things better left unspoken.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056101_MSG0028
rows.name:
What matters is that friend saved Mira from threat.
For that, Divine Nopopon thank you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056101_MSG0029
rows.name: Friend has done well.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056101_MSG0045
rows.name:
Divine Nopopon hears sounds nearby from that which
should not be here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056101_MSG0046
rows.name:
...But it not seem to be doing bad things.
If it merely annoying, that is probably okay.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056101_MSG0047
rows.name:
Because of friend, great menace has been quieted.
For that, Divine Nopopon thanks you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056101_MSG0048
rows.name: Friend has done well.[ST:wait ]
